# Minimal Apple Music/App Store exceptions routed through the proxy.
# PacketTunnel log evidence: direct TCP connections to these exact hosts
# repeatedly timed out after about 5 seconds, while other Apple hosts worked.

# App Store catalog and configuration.
DOMAIN,amp-api-edge.apps.apple.com
DOMAIN,amp-api-updates.apps.apple.com
DOMAIN,bag.itunes.apple.com
DOMAIN,pd.itunes.apple.com
DOMAIN,itunes.apple.com

# Apple Music catalog.
DOMAIN,amp-api.music.apple.com

# App Store / Music static assets.
DOMAIN,is1-ssl.mzstatic.com
